  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382070/extras/94d57dcd0df2bceab8d6a8e0eb53ac9b.poster.avif?t=1764842475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382070/extras/94d57dcd0df2bceab8d6a8e0eb53ac9b.webm?t=1764842475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382070/extras/94d57dcd0df2bceab8d6a8e0eb53ac9b.mp4?t=1764842475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Challenge perception, redefine reality, and reshape the world around you with an instant camera. <strong>Viewfinder</strong> is a new single player game offering gamers hours of interesting and fun experiences while uncovering the mysteries left behind.<br><br><strong>Viewfinder</strong> is a mind-bending first person adventure game in which you can bring pictures to life by placing them into the world. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Reshape Reality: Beyond photographs, bring paintings, sketches, screenshots and postcards to life while reshaping the world<br></li><li>Exploration is learning: You will learn the secrets of the world, the reason why it exists, and the freedom to create. Explore multiple hub worlds that are all cohesive and encompass similar, but complex, differences<br></li><li>Experience as much as you want: <strong>Viewfinder’s</strong> narrative is player driven and will be an approachable experience to someone who just wants to play and solve puzzles, and a rich well thought off world to a player who wants to learn more<br></li><li>Find the answer to the impossible, once you step in the world of <strong>Viewfinder</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382070/extras/580a00d85beebfb80efefd04d6cd8664.poster.avif?t=1764842475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382070/extras/580a00d85beebfb80efefd04d6cd8664.webm?t=1764842475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382070/extras/580a00d85beebfb80efefd04d6cd8664.mp4?t=1764842475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382070/extras/94d57dcd0df2bceab8d6a8e0eb53ac9b.poster.avif?t=1764842475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382070/extras/94d57dcd0df2bceab8d6a8e0eb53ac9b.webm?t=1764842475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382070/extras/94d57dcd0df2bceab8d6a8e0eb53ac9b.mp4?t=1764842475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Challenge perception, redefine reality, and reshape the world around you with an instant camera. <strong>Viewfinder</strong> is a new single player game offering gamers hours of interesting and fun experiences while uncovering the mysteries left behind.<br><br><strong>Viewfinder</strong> is a mind-bending first person adventure game in which you can bring pictures to life by placing them into the world. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Reshape Reality: Beyond photographs, bring paintings, sketches, screenshots and postcards to life while reshaping the world<br></li><li>Exploration is learning: You will learn the secrets of the world, the reason why it exists, and the freedom to create. Explore multiple hub worlds that are all cohesive and encompass similar, but complex, differences<br></li><li>Experience as much as you want: <strong>Viewfinder’s</strong> narrative is player driven and will be an approachable experience to someone who just wants to play and solve puzzles, and a rich well thought off world to a player who wants to learn more<br></li><li>Find the answer to the impossible, once you step in the world of <strong>Viewfinder</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382070/extras/580a00d85beebfb80efefd04d6cd8664.poster.avif?t=1764842475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382070/extras/580a00d85beebfb80efefd04d6cd8664.webm?t=1764842475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382070/extras/580a00d85beebfb80efefd04d6cd8664.mp4?t=1764842475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
